BIG NOTE: nActionType These constants are the SH_cls_Execute, SH_cls_Disconnect, nReprepare,
  SH_cls_Commit, SH_cls_Rollback are the values MUST be 2,4,8,16,32,64,128,256 etc and
  nLess20OkDontAsk OR nLess20NotOkDontAsk must also have a value in this sequence.
IF the application does not want the message "Item is less than 20! Continue YES/NO" to
  be asked then OR together SH_cls_Execute | nLess20OkDontAsk OR SH_cls_Execute | nLess20NotOkDontAsk
  to asume a no user interaction action.  By default the message will be asked!
ALSO Assumed is that nLess20OkDontAsk and nLess20NotOkDontAsk will not be used
  together in the one OR statement.
